name: Introvert Club #1
description:
Post Party Syndroma (@postpartysyndroma) is an online archiving platform for the party scene. Runs as a non-profit collective, and utilize the open-culture, we use Creative Commons License Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International (CC BY-SA 4.0)

Introvert Club is a place where an introverted person can go party comfortably and secure. Because everyone can be themself in here, welcomed without being judged.

Photo taken by @postpartysyndroma, 3D works @arthropochan & @sanj0nas, minted by @chandraakbar
All sales will be use for collective operational during the event. And will be burnt on 5 PM 10th December 2021
